{"tid":1743517,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［連登仔？］ 叔本華 論女人","createTime":"2019-11-21T08:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T07:15:10.000Z","uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b01722ed6240cdfac6b8af87e2ea29b6b9db96c7","tid":1743517,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:39:50.000Z","msg":"「女人適合做護士和幼師，恰恰由於她們本來就幼稚、愚蠢、目光短淺。一句話，女人終其一生都是大孩子，位於孩子和男人之間的過渡階段。男人才是真正的人。」&mdash;&mdash;叔本華，〈論女人〉<br />\n<br />\n「偽裝是女人根深蒂固的天性，最愚蠢的女人和最聰明的女人在這方面往往一樣。女人一有機會就偽裝，這對她們來說就像動物一遇攻擊就採取防衛一樣天經地義，而且她偽裝時感覺好像只是在行使她的權利。不去偽裝、完全真實的女人幾乎沒有。正因為這樣，女人能輕易地看穿他人的偽裝，想在女人面前裝假委實不明智。&hellip;&hellip;做偽證的女人要比男人多得多，是否應該允許女人宣誓都值得懷疑。」&mdash;&mdash;叔本華，〈論女人〉<br />\n<br />\n「女人基本上只為種族的繁衍而活，並以此為全部事業，所以他們更關注種族而不是個體，心裡也以種族為重，個體為輕。」&mdash;&mdash;叔本華，〈論女人〉<br />\n<br />\n好似又有D道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://read01.com/zh-hk/6xD38a.html#.XdZMwkUzYWo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2Fzh-hk%2F6xD38a.html%23.XdZMwkUzYWo&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameA3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=8ed5d79d\" target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/zh-hk/6xD38a.html#.XdZMwkUzYWo</a>"},{"pid":"227ae98461f39638b0e39c09e28ca261f8777928","tid":1743517,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U84oZn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU84oZn6.jpg&h=065a56a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMbyB1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMbyB1k.jpg&h=604a5751&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期五夜晚，各區商場和理非唱歌，區選前最大型和理非行動，想問下你會唔會參與？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"75148af6a8c71c9b3e4634548bfcc7cfc2cb072d","tid":1743517,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"